submission.source: I am Kenyan citizen living in Kenya. Managing a fund for friends, family and extended family that has taken 6 years to build up. We are average people in Kenya where the money invested represent many years salary. I was planning to quit my miserable job and manage this full time but this hack did not only destroy those plans, it also put myself in $200k in debt and unsure without your choosing, how I will ever recover so much to so many while surely everyone will hate me. I have been in darkness since this happened but some hope has returned when I saw your message that you have honour and principles in your actions. I would be deeply grateful if the amount was returned. (I can verify everything in my message and we are not rich American or Europeans)
